Interface MultiPart.Parser.Listener

All Known Implementing Classes:
MultiPart.AbstractPartsListener
Enclosing class:
MultiPart.Parser
public static interface MultiPart.Parser.Listener

A listener for events emitted by a MultiPart.Parser.
